name: src/components/button/button.component.js

properties.name: type
properties.description: binding symbol is @, 此类型针对的是样式, 比如选了primary class会出现 `bp-btn-primary`, 默认值是primary, 可选值[default, primary, danger]

properties.name: size
properties.description: binding symbol is @, 按钮大小, 和bootstrap一样, 不填则是默认大小

properties.name: htmlType
properties.description: binding symbol is @, 顾名思义, 代表的是原生html里的type值

properties.name: disabled
properties.description: binding symbol is <, 禁用状态

properties.name: icon
properties.description: binding symbol is @, 按钮文字前方的icon名称, 详细见bootstrap

properties.name: click
properties.description: binding symbol is &, click 处理器

CheckboxGroup
description: checkbox group
examples:
<bp-checkbox-group model="vm.groupDataList"></bp-checkbox-group>
groupDataList = [
{label: '邢老师不要脸', checked: true},
{label: '老师不要脸'},
{label: '师不要脸'},
{label: '不要脸'},
{label: '要脸', disabled: true},
{label: '脸'}
];

Component
description: 基类, 定义了模板和一系列基础操作

name: _state
description: every component has a state object,  according to the state properties to determine how to display UI

name: _init
description: 是否初始化完毕, 标识着是否执行完$onInit

name: state
description: get component state

name: state
description: set component state

name: $onInit
description: 构建模板, 在最后会将 _init设置为true

name: _initDefaultValue
description: 初始化默认值, 因为angular组件变量传递是在component定义决定的, 有些值可能没有传进来, 所以在这里确定一次

name: _initDefaultState
description: initialize state object

name: _createClassName
description:
确定className, 处理过之后赋值到`this.className`属性, 并经由此属性填充到UI(html)的class属性里
每次render都会重新计算一次样式

name: _launch
description: 实现组件功能的细节部分

name: _render
description: 针对不同的状态, 做UI变化, 如果子类有新状态那么override, 并super调用此方法
